Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:06.78,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}为何想要忘却？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:12.76,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}请回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:24.43,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}那温暖的脸颊上滑落而下的泪之请愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:31.03,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}为何你在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:36.59,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}现在寻求着何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:43.22,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}只有你无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.97,0:23:48.91,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}都想与你相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:55.29,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蔚蓝的星海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:24:01.17,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}波浪间漂浮的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.28,0:24:07.23,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}渐渐逝去的悲痛是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.30,0:24:12.81,ED_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向着明日的祈祷


